fields.description:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Create a new project in TiStudio called debug_test
2. Move the js files form the debug test project in titanium_mobile_tests_internal
3. Follow steps in test case 1013 from http://wiki.appcelerator.org/display/tp/Debugger+Test+Plan

Result: After step 10, extra data is being printed out to the console. See attachment.
Expected: The extra data should not be printed out to the console.

Note: The extra data does not appear in V8 or in 1.7.5
fields.summary: Android: Rhino Debugger - Extra data is being printed out to the console
